      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-maintained over the years. It's perfect for someone looking for a reliable car that still looks great on the road and handles like a dream. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
